{"tid":1492251,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《Marvel上氣》涉辱華爭議 梁朝偉向迪士尼反映","createTime":"2019-08-20T17:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T11:22:36.000Z","uid":147837,"like":109,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"503b0a660f323032e38fb3997b6d3dc828cdbaae","tid":1492251,"uid":147837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:54:10.000Z","msg":"Marvel Studios於上月的SDCC公佈開拍《上氣：The Legend of the Ten Rings》，並由梁朝偉飾演反派滿大人，可惜一眾中國影迷就狠批梁朝偉接演，認為角色有辱華成份，打算擺看電影。<br />\n<br />\n而日前與梁朝偉在新片《風再起時》中合作的香港導演翁子光透露，梁朝偉本人已經看到了網友們的爭議，已經向迪士尼反映。<br />\n<br />\n翁子光認爲這樣的爭議對梁朝偉很不公平，希望觀眾應該看到電影成品再評價，認為一眾影迷只是「羊群心理」，沒有獨立地思考。<br />\n<br />\n   「他（梁朝偉）說跟迪士尼已經反映過了，他們特別注意這個事。所以這個人物，不會是觀眾想像的辱華。怎麼可能呢，人家Marvel不想來內地嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/269368053088280/posts/3199405023417887?s=100006351210974&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F269368053088280%2Fposts%2F3199405023417887%3Fs%3D100006351210974%26sfns%3Dmo&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41ANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=8e7eee1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/269368053088280/posts/3199405023417887?s=100006351210974&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HenHK6M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHenHK6M.png&h=6d1ee9c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又玻璃心發作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe85c1541a20ef6ce12ed80cb957af4f10229b7a","tid":1492251,"uid":68483,"like":220,"dislike":0,"score":220,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T18:12:10.000Z","msg":"華人做奸角就係辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔諗下你拍啲葉問，戰狼搵咩人做反派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd75f31aaadf5d04a4215ddd3c757f5131271bd9","tid":1492251,"uid":36702,"like":96,